Technology
Lecture will largely be a low tech affair: pencil and paper should be sufficient most of the time. You should always plan to bring a laptop or tablet device to lab. In general, you will need access to a device with internet so that you can use the following:

This course page that you are on right now;
R/RStudio via the Duke Container Manager;
Canvas, through which you can access…

Gradescope;
